flowchart TD
  Start([Load Called]) --> SetDefaults
  SetDefaults --> GetPaths[Get Config Paths]
  GetPaths --> PathsError{Error?}
  PathsError -->|Yes| ReturnErr[Return nil, error]
  PathsError -->|No| AddPaths[Add each dir to viper]
  AddPaths --> ReadConfig[viper.ReadInConfig]
  ReadConfig --> ReadErr{Error?}
  ReadErr -->|ConfigFileNotFound| Continue[Continue with defaults]
  ReadErr -->|Other error| ReturnErr
  Continue --> BindEnv[SetEnvPrefix & AutomaticEnv]
  ReadErr -->|No error| BindEnv
  BindEnv --> Unmarshal[viper.Unmarshal]
  Unmarshal --> UnmarshalErr{Error?}
  UnmarshalErr -->|Yes| ReturnErr
  UnmarshalErr -->|No| ReturnCfg[Return &cfg, nil]
